Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.98,sign_24_1_The_Third_Dish,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Plate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:02.98,sign_24_2_Two,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Two
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:05.81,sign_72_3_Moon_Festival_Gu,,0000,0000,0000,,Moon Festival Guide Book
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.57,0:00:08.00,Main Dialogue,Mitsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Come get the {\i1}Moon Festival Guide Book{\i0},\N hot off the press!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:09.28,Main Dialogue,Mitsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Get one, take one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:10.99,Main Dialogue,Mitsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:13.65,Main Dialogue,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:15.99,Main Dialogue,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Is Yukihira Soma for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:20.14,Italics Dialogue,Mitsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira-senpai, I put you \Nright where you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:23.21,Italics Dialogue,Mitsuru,0000,0000,0000,,I had the article about your booth set
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:26.33,sign_561_12_Totsuki_Academy_,Sign 0026,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki Academy High School Division 1st Year, Yukihira Soma
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:26.33,Italics Dialogue,Mitsuru,0000,0000,0000,,right on the next page after \Nthe Chinese Cuisine RS!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:28.98,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,He's setting up right in \Nfront of the Chinese Cuisine RS?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:31.41,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,And he's going to serve Chinese food?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:34.21,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,And he had to get his booth listed \Nright next to their page, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.90,0:00:36.18,Main Dialogue,I,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't surprise me one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.57,0:00:39.89,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I figured he'd start something \Nup to stir the pot,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:42.64,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't expect him to \Ntake them on head-on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:46.06,Main Dialogue,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.45,0:00:49.35,Main Dialogue,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,You always fire me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.35,0:00:51.85,Main Dialogue,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, you're crushing the guidebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.85,0:00:52.57,Main Dialogue,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:54.02,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:00:55.82,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Yukihira-kun get all the attention?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:58.53,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Yukihira-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.49,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,You look so chill, but you're so extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:05.96,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you won't come to regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:23.72,sign_6424_110_Food_Wars,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(316,232)}Food Wars
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:23.72,sign_6424_111_The_Third_Plate,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(316,232)}The Third Plate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:40.26,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,"You know you'll get expelled\Nif your booth loses money, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:44.83,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,When Nakiri said that,\NI did get kind of spooked,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.97,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,but thinking about it, how can\NI end up with zero profit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:51.00,sign_4004_33__Ma__and__La_,Sign 0248,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(503,476)}"Ma" and "La"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:51.74,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's a huge five-day festival \Nthat'll have 500,000 people coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:53.44,Main Dialogue,Konishi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:03:00.29,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you decide to set up shop \Nright in front of a powerful competitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:03.66,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure it'll all work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.88,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't sound convincing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.48,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,I know how disorganized you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:09.35,Main Dialogue,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:10.12,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.74,Main Dialogue,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ikumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:13.38,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Can you check the paperwork, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:15.43,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:18.84,Main Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ikumi-senpai's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:23.12,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Don RS sure is booming these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:27.22,Main Dialogue,Konishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're getting a ton of applicants \Nfrom the junior high division.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:31.23,Main Dialogue,Konishi,0000,0000,0000,,Nikumi's gotten way more charismatic lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:35.66,Main Dialogue,Konishi,0000,0000,0000,,She won the Shokugeki against Sadatsuka Nao\N without any trouble, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:37.15,sign_5135_50_S_a_d_a_t_s_u_k_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,S\Na\Nd\Na\Nt\Ns\Nu\Nk\Na\N \NN\Na\No\N \N(White)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:37.15,sign_5159_51_B_u_r_n_e_d___O_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,B\Nu\Nr\Nn\Ne\Nd-\N\NO\Nu\Nt\N \NV\Ne\Nr\Ns\Ni\No\Nn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.70,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Yukihira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:39.20,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:42.69,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to help out at your booth,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:46.31,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,but I have to take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:47.66,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:50.13,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's no need, Nikumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:52.90,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who told you to \Ngive Don RS your best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:54.49,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:56.96,Main Dialogue,Ikumi,0000,0000,0000,,But if you run into any trouble,\Nask for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.21,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:00.05,Main Dialogue,Konishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what Nikumi said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:05.05,Main Dialogue,Konishi,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you and Tadokoro \Nare honorary members!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.01,sign_5876_65_H_o_n_o_r_a_r_y_,Sign 0407,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(238,1)}H\No\Nn\No\Nr\Na\Nr\Ny\N \Nm\Ne\Nm\Nb\Ne\Nr\Ns\N?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.01,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,We are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:10.78,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I gotta do what I gotta do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.81,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous, Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:13.23,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:15.81,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to get so mad at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:19.15,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,The booth application deadline \Nwas a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:21.82,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,You decide now that you want\N to join the Moon Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:25.32,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I may be one of the Elite Ten, \Nbut even I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.82,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:30.53,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,I can grab someone else's booth \Nlocation using a Shokugeki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:31.81,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,There are other ways, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:34.04,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,You said it was too much trouble\Nto even bother last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:37.27,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you Nakiris fighting about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:38.83,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukihira-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:40.25,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call us that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:42.01,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.87,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Due to traffic,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:47.01,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,the contractors handling interior \Nconstruction will be an hour late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.55,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I suppose we can't do much about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:48.95,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:50.39,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you guys time to spare, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:51.27,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:54.97,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking that I'm gonna make \Nsome dishes I used to serve back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:56.65,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Can you be taste testers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:57.67,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.87,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I do something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:02.11,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Just for an hour, Yukihira!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:03.86,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama is very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:05.86,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hisako isn't vetoing it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:07.37,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,I can chip in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:08.87,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:16.00,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,I've sliced the green onions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.90,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,That's as far as I'll go in terms of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.17,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:20.84,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hisako...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:23.92,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not wrong. I think she's friendlier \Nwith Yukihira-kun lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:26.82,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hisako...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:27.63,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.89,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing. Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:35.27,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the Yukihira-Style Mapo Tofu Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.73,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.10,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,From what I've seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:41.61,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,this appears to be a typical dish served \Nat restaurants for the general public,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:42.67,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Erina-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:54.12,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.74,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,So spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.74,0:05:59.07,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,But this won't let you beat Kuga-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:03.59,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,That's because your dish lacks both \Nma and la by a significant margin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:08.26,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,"Ma" and "la"? What are \Nyou talking about, Nakiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.01,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,You should be ashamed of your ignorance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:14.01,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, spiciness in Chinese \Ncuisine rests upon two pillars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:17.89,Main Dialogue Top,E,0000,0000,0000,,The fiery spiciness associated \Nwith red chili peppers, la-wei,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:18.04,sign_9034_119_La_wei,Sign 0618,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(253,246)}La-wei
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.98,Main Dialogue Top,E,0000,0000,0000,,and the numbing spiciness associated \Nwith Sichuan peppers, ma-wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:21.75,sign_9034_119_La_wei,Sign 0621,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(256,244)}Ma-wei
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:24.53,Main Dialogue Top,E,0000,0000,0000,,The two combined are called ma-la-wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.04,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:26.90,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sichuan peppers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:30.53,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Nikumi used them during the prelims.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:35.29,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Chinese cuisine encompasses \Na very broad range of dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:38.70,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,There are eight great regional \Ncuisines across China,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:44.63,sign_9502_124_Anui__,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(503,1)}Anui
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:44.63,sign_9526_125_Hunan,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(503,1)}Hunan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:44.63,sign_9549_126_Jiangsu,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(503,1)}Jiangsu
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:41.60,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,each of which developed in a specific \Nclimate and local customs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:44.63,sign_9574_127_Fujian,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(503,1)}Fujian
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:44.63,sign_9598_128_Zhejiang,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(503,1)}Zhejiang
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:44.63,sign_9622_129_Shandong,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(503,1)}Shandong
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:44.63,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,The ma-la flavor is considered \Nthe distinctive characteristic
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:44.63,sign_9670_131_Sichuan,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(503,1)}Sichuan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:50.43,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,of Sichuan cuisine,\N which is Kuga-senpai's forte—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:50.78,sign_9702_135_Sichuan,Sign 0646,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,287)}Sichuan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.67,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:52.35,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:54.22,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I gave him useful information!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:56.75,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That was really helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:58.73,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for explaining it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.45,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,F-Forget what I just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:02.36,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Forget everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.58,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:04.74,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:06.99,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible, Erina-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:09.53,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.24,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,So Chinese Cuisine RS's mapo tofu has all that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:13.58,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,lingering flavor despite \Nthe sheer spiciness of it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:17.20,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,because Kuga-senpai is making \Ngood use of the ma-la flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.53,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:21.01,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,His culinary skills are \Nquite advanced, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:25.42,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,but there can be yet another reason \Nwhy his spiciness is so addictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:26.13,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:30.38,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,From a biological standpoint,\Nspiciness is not about the sense of taste,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:32.38,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,but about the sense of pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:35.51,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, so it's about how much it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.42,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:40.05,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Spiciness is not sensed by \Nthe same flavor receptors
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:42.39,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,that handle sweetness, bitterness, \Nsourness, saltiness, and umami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.98,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,It's sensed by a separate \Nclass of vanilloid receptors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.26,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Extra strong spiciness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:50.65,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,also causes adrenaline and beta-endorphins \Nto be released in the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:54.55,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Those neurotransmitters trigger \Nfeelings of excitement and happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:57.53,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,That'd explain why spiciness is addictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:01.21,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's only possible because \Nspiciness is perceived as pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:03.40,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,In medicinal cuisine,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:06.16,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,spiciness is said to aid internal \Norgans in their functions
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:08.59,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,and also help reduce stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:10.33,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:15.25,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,That's why those who wield absolute control \Nover spiciness are formidable foes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:17.76,Main Dialogue,Hisako,0000,0000,0000,,Kuga-san once said to me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.05,Flashback Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,When anyone eats my food,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:22.90,Flashback Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,they all sweat a ton and turn \Nred in the face, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.07,Flashback Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,But they all keep eating anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:26.94,Flashback Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing that is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:33.20,Flashback Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,I love torturing people with my food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.37,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can kind of relate to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:37.85,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,When someone eats my food and \Nsmiles because it tastes good
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:40.38,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,or groans because it tastes awful, it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:42.53,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's part of why I cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:45.67,Italics Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,I see he's plenty twisted enough on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:49.49,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, spiciness can deliver a jolt \Nof delicious flavor like lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:53.42,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Kuga-senpai is well aware of how \Nit can bring people to their knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:56.93,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,That's how he was able to join the Elite Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:59.80,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,The overwhelming spiciness of Sichuan cuisine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.10,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,and its underlying complex flavors—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:05.00,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,if you do not have a \Nmeans of countering that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:06.77,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,you will never be able to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:08.77,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:11.45,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Nakiri-san said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:17.20,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Is your mapo tofu so bad, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.95,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's not "bad,"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:24.11,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,but it's true that it can't stand \Nup the spiciness of Sichuan cuisine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:28.02,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's a similar to back when \NI clashed with Mimasaka over beef stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.95,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I guess testing is the \Nonly way I'll find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:34.63,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'm going to research \Nthe heck out of that spiciness,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.78,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,then I'm going to figure out \Na recipe that'll let me win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:38.01,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:40.39,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this might be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:42.47,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I brought Chinese recipes and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:43.56,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:46.67,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you get invited by \NIsshiki-senpai to join in
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:48.63,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,on the Polar Star Dormitory \Nbooth with the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:49.35,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:54.22,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,My Regional Cuisine RS is doing a booth, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.07,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,But I turned both of them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.70,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:58.72,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.58,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean, I thought you \Ndidn't have enough staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.90,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um... Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.42,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I might hold you back, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:12.46,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,B-But back home, I'd help out with customers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.38,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,and I studied up some \Nduring the Stagiaire, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:17.63,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I think I might \Nbe of some help, maybe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:21.27,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,So... if I can help you with your booth...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:23.56,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,That is, if you're okay with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:26.81,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Tadokoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:28.52,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That'd seriously be a super big help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:29.85,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:33.25,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's cook up something \Nawesome, Tadokoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:34.57,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.02,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:38.57,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,May I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:40.78,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.69,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:47.75,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,I, Nakiri Alice, have decided to\Nparticipate in the Moon Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.58,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:53.29,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,But the booth application period has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:55.13,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,So let's put our best foot forward together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.13,Italics Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:11:00.04,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use the Shiomi Research Group's booth \Nlocation together, with the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:04.37,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,I have permission from Professor Shiomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:05.35,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:07.89,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Please hear me out, Professor Shiomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:11.63,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,He can continue his work at \Nthe Shiomi Research Group,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:13.46,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,but he can only participate \Nin the school festival
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:15.67,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,as a high school first year\N once in his lifetime!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:17.23,Flashback Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Once in his lifetime...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:22.29,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,It is our wish to create something \Nmemorable together with Akira-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:25.71,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,our valued school friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:27.24,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Ryo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:27.91,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.05,Flashback Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,"Our valued school friend"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:33.42,sign_16494_245_Maternal_Instinc,Sign 1129,0000,0000,0000,,Maternal Instinct
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:33.42,Flashback Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama-kun has friends his own age!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:36.74,Flashback Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,So on that note, please sign this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:39.17,sign_16722_249_Shiomi_Jun,Sign 1139,0000,0000,0000,,Shiomi Jun
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:39.17,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,That Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:41.34,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Now do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.86,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and of course, I will be the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:45.21,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a given!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:46.35,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,To heck with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:49.32,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Kurokiba, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.32,0:11:51.59,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Once the miss is set on something,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:53.06,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,you can't stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.33,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:55.19,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Tough it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.58,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, Yukihira-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:58.65,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Erina!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:01.32,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to one-up you guys at the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:05.01,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you know that our booth \Nlocation is in the Main Avenue area,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:07.33,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,so it's not where Yukihira \Nor Nakiri Erina will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.54,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,What? How tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.79,sign_17492_266_Missing,,0000,0000,0000,,Polar Star Dormitory
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:15.03,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,First, saute ground pork over high heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:18.42,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Boil firm tofu for two \Nminutes and let it drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:22.17,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Once the ground pork turns \Nbrown and fragrant,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:23.55,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,add the spicy flavors!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:26.21,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Take chicken stock and add sweet bean sauce,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:27.90,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,chili bean sauce, black bean sauce,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:30.22,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,garlic, and chili powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.23,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:34.98,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's still not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:38.15,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't the spiciness I \Ntasted at Chinese Cuisine RS.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.07,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:44.20,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.27,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.41,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.71,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Not gonna let them beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:48.66,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, it's spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:50.87,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I did it, Tadokoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:53.90,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Mapo Tofu, Extra Spicy Version!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.71,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Try it, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:59.09,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,His lips are already swollen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:10.57,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shpicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.77,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's ridiculously spicy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:16.65,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's try some other Chinese dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:18.10,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Twice-cooked pork.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:19.65,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Pepper steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:23.21,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry, Tadokoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:24.78,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,You can take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:27.99,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have to do the tasting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:30.49,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shpicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:32.06,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I ate it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:34.96,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to eat it, Soma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:36.01,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.79,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,but it's still a complete failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:41.05,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,They're just spicy, and that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:44.71,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond all that spiciness,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:48.64,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,the Chinese Cuisine RS's mapo \Ntofu had well-constructed umami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:53.26,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Soma-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:55.10,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I heard this from Hojo-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:58.66,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,but the seasonings used \Nby the Chinese Cuisine RS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:01.55,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,like chili bean sauce,\N sweet bean sauce, black bean sauce,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:06.74,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,and oyster sauce are all \Nspecially-made by Kuga-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.19,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Specially-made?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:13.00,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's why there's so much \Numami underlying the spiciness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:14.45,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:17.25,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,So one of Sichuan cuisine's signature dishes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:18.85,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,has been infused with multiple expressions
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:20.27,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,of Kuga-senpai's culinary convictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:22.96,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's really become a dish that \Nrepresents who he is as a chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:25.70,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Spiciness, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.76,sign_20891_317_Missing,,0000,0000,0000,,Skewers RS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:41.43,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:45.19,sign_21092_318_An_Evening_of_Ta,Sign 1440,0000,0000,0000,,An Evening of Taro Stew\N With Isshiki Satoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:42.24,Main Dialogue,I,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:45.19,Main Dialogue,I,0000,0000,0000,,Our Polar Star Dormitory booth \Nwill be serving taro stew!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:46.19,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.90,Main Dialogue,I,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be using a lot of produce \Ngrown on the Isshiki farm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.90,sign_21263_323_An_Evening_of_Ta,Sign 1440,0000,0000,0000,,An Evening of Taro Stew\NWith Isshiki Satoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:51.16,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The booth sign's well-made, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:53.41,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I designed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:55.37,Main Dialogue,Aoki-Sato,0000,0000,0000,,We built it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:59.12,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure using a temporary tent in the \Nhigh-class Yamanote Area is a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:02.13,Main Dialogue,Ryoko,0000,0000,0000,,We're hoping to look rustic and approachable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:04.11,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We already have a ton of advance reservations
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:08.34,Main Dialogue,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,from ladies who attend \NIsshiki-senpai's cooking class!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.49,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I get that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:12.55,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you dressed like \Nthat, Isshiki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:17.43,Main Dialogue,I,0000,0000,0000,,Well, traditional taro stew gatherings \Nare done on a river bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.35,Main Dialogue,I,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm thinking right around there, say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:21.90,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Does he intend to put a river there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.51,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of paint!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:24.14,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,We need a purchase run, stat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:24.72,Main Dialogue,Students,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone available to help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:27.51,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, everyone's in all-out prep mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:30.98,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Every day after school will be like this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.58,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:33.99,Main Dialogue,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,Tadokoro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.38,Main Dialogue,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:35.83,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.07,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Isami-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:39.59,sign_22461_347_Pop_Up,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(386,1)}Pop-Up
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:39.59,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,"Pop-up Trattoria Aldini"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:40.79,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:41.83,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing it with Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:44.26,Main Dialogue,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,With all of our classmates, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:45.13,Main Dialogue,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:48.38,Main Dialogue,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you're going to \Nchallenge Kuga-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.23,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:50.63,Main Dialogue,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,Let me say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:54.09,Main Dialogue,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the only one who's \Ngrown during the Stagiaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:56.85,Main Dialogue,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think I'm the same man \NI was during the prelims!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:59.07,Main Dialogue,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who'll defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:01.38,Main Dialogue,Isami,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go shopping, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:03.99,Main Dialogue,Takumi,0000,0000,0000,,You hear me, Yukihira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:05.27,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:07.14,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,The menu's already set!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:11.01,sign_23144_362_Shiomi_Research_,Sign 1607,0000,0000,0000,,Shiomi Research Group \N Creative Curry Laboratory
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:08.09,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:09.90,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it have to be curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:13.28,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,We're inviting representatives from\NShiomi Research Group's corporate partners!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:14.78,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:17.78,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Then why am I even showing up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:20.00,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message from Professor Shiomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:23.61,Italics Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I'll manage our corporate partners somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:26.38,Italics Dialogue,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama-kun, go enjoy student life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.21,Main Dialogue,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Jun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:31.27,Main Dialogue Top,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Professor Shiomi told me to \Ncollaborate with you on the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:30.02,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's a fun trio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:32.22,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they'll actually \Nbe able to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:33.76,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's busy everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.63,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess everyone's enjoying student life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:38.10,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's really invigorating!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.25,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, march!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:43.33,Italics Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing invigorating about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:44.25,Main Dialogue Top,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,A one-two, a one-two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.60,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukihira-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.74,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:48.34,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is that construction material for your booth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:50.33,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's such a production.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:52.22,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,Our booth's huge,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:54.49,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,and the storefront is an \Nimportant factor, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:56.74,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It kind of looks grim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:59.95,Main Dialogue,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all! We're having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.20,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:04.22,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,Still, if your booth loses money,\Nyou'll be expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:07.86,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't possibly bear \Nto see young talent like you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:10.11,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,forced to leave the academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:12.17,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're definitely not thinking that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:16.78,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,Well, try not to get expelled, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:17.45,Main Dialogue Top,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, march!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:22.13,Main Dialogue Top,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,A one-two, a one-two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:22.43,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,The storefront's also an \Nimportant factor, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:25.25,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that when I set up shop \Nat a summer festival with Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:27.81,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,we got more customers when \Nwe were more creative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:29.11,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.60,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:32.49,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Nakiri said it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:34.66,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sichuan isn't the only Chinese cuisine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.86,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe, just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:39.95,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Tadokoro, there's something I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:40.99,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Can you help?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:43.16,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:45.04,sign_25491_410_Chinese_Cuisine_,Sign 1744,0000,0000,0000,,Chinese Cuisine Culinary Division \N Warehouse No. 3
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:48.17,Main Dialogue,Miyoko,0000,0000,0000,,This is what Yukihira wants, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:49.88,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:52.38,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay to let us use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:53.56,Main Dialogue,Miyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:56.98,Main Dialogue,Miyoko,0000,0000,0000,,I already got permission from the \Nlead lecturer in Chinese cuisine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:18:00.72,Main Dialogue,Miyoko,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to hit me up if \Nyou needed help, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:02.18,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:05.55,Main Dialogue,Miyoko,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could help you out \Nduring the festival, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:07.56,Main Dialogue,Miyoko,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm supposed to help \Nout at a different booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:10.68,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about it \Nafter all your help already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:14.10,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're still training for \Nyour family restaurant, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:16.99,Main Dialogue,Miyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's all baby steps,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:20.20,Main Dialogue,Miyoko,0000,0000,0000,,but I feel I'm building better relationships \Nwith the restaurant staff lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:22.72,Main Dialogue,Miyoko,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can be like you soon—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:25.16,Main Dialogue,Miyoko,0000,0000,0000,,a chef everyone likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.79,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:28.92,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it go, Tadokoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.25,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Soma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:31.79,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Found it! Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:34.31,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks, Hojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:35.32,Main Dialogue,Miyoko,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:38.53,Main Dialogue,Miyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you give Kuga-san a \Nrun for his money with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:39.63,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.60,Flashback Dialogue,SBoy,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:46.36,Flashback Dialogue,SDad,0000,0000,0000,,It's a stone oven I borrowed \Nfrom someone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:49.30,Flashback Dialogue,SDad,0000,0000,0000,,If we just do pan-fried noodles \Nevery year, it gets boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:53.94,Flashback Dialogue,SDad,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use this to get top sales \Nat this year's summer festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:55.64,Flashback Dialogue,SBoy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:58.03,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,We need this to get it all started...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.49,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,in order to make {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:02.53,sign_27358_441_A_Few_Days_Later,Sign 1902,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(527,1)}A Few Days Later
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:07.50,sign_27400_442_Moon_Festival_Op,Sign 1905,0000,0000,0000,,Moon Festival Opening Day
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:06.71,Main Dialogue Top,Urara,0000,0000,0000,,The plum ticket is 500 yen,\Nthe bamboo ticket is 1,000 yen,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:09.34,Main Dialogue Top,Urara,0000,0000,0000,,and the pine ticket is 10,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:13.67,Main Dialogue,Urara,0000,0000,0000,,Customers will use these \Ntickets at your booths!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:13.67,sign_27572_448_Totsuki,,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:16.89,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,They serve as proofs of purchase,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:19.65,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,so please don't lose them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:24.93,Main Dialogue,Urara,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, your earnings report must be \Nsubmitted before 6:00 PM every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:25.43,sign_27928_449_Missing,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,600)}Te-he!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:25.64,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Te-he!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:29.07,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira-kun... Erina, you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:29.52,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:31.92,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,The day's finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:33.81,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:36.02,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:36.81,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:37.81,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:40.94,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disappointed that I can't compete \Nin the same area as you two,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:45.01,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,but our booth will beat out the rest of \Nothe competition in the Main Avenue area.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:47.75,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,The two behind you seem to be \Nsuffering from extreme fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:50.38,Main Dialogue,E,0000,0000,0000,,Is your booth going to be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:51.79,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:54.58,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Yukihira-kun, don't let \Nyour rival get you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:55.82,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck with everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:58.76,Main Dialogue,Alice,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, speak of the devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:08.64,Main Dialogue,Urara,0000,0000,0000,,We'll now sing the Totsuki Teahouse \NCulinary Academy's school anthem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:11.83,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,School anthem? We have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:12.81,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know, Tadokoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:20.78,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Here in the bosom of the \Nland of the rising sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:28.70,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,come ye sharp and bright-souled youths
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:33.07,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Look upon the pinnacle of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:36.83,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Now, bestir yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:41.17,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, hone yourselves. (Hone yourselves.)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:45.02,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,You are in the sacred land of gourmands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:53.61,Italics Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,You are here in Totsuki Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:51.20,sign_29914_478_92_Annual_Moon_F,,0000,0000,0000,,The 92nd\N{\fs30\c&H0000C5&}Moon Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:55.27,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukassan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:59.37,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll keep your promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:03.40,Main Dialogue,Senzaemon,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:12.04,Main Dialogue,Senzaemon,0000,0000,0000,,I now announce the opening \Nof the Moon Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:14.77,sign_29914_478_92_Annual_Moon_F,Sign 2112,0000,0000,0000,,The 92nd\N{\fs30\c&H0000C5&}Moon Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:17.96,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,If I may say so myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:20.04,sign_30613_484_Kuga_Restaurant,Sign 2119,0000,0000,0000,,Kuga Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:20.04,Main Dialogue,Kuga,0000,0000,0000,,I've created one very \Nrespectable restaurant here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.04,0:21:21.06,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:24.93,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at Yukihira Soma's \Nbooth in comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.51,sign_30817_489_Totsuki_Culinary,Sign 2126,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuki Culinary Teahouse Academy \N{\fs18\c&H685BB6&}Famous Taiwanese\N Black Pepper Buns
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:28.97,Main Dialogue,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,How dare he even consider \Nchallenging us with such a place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:32.06,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:36.15,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,This is our first hand to win \Nagainst the Chinese Cuisine RS—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:38.35,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,the black pepper bun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.11,0:23:00.73,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Piping hot black pepper buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.16,0:23:03.66,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a hot black pepper bun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.66,0:23:04.29,Main Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:05.69,Main Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,Black pepper buns?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:06.95,Main Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:09.49,Main Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,They're famous Taiwanese street food, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:11.36,Main Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.36,0:23:14.32,Main Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,They're plastered all over \Ninside the stone oven!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.32,0:23:15.58,Main Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what they taste like?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.99,0:23:20.58,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,They have a ground pork rib meat \Nfilling seasoned with black pepper!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:22.68,Main Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I want to try that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.68,0:23:23.38,Main Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:24.25,Main Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,Give me two!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:25.96,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:27.59,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:29.34,Main Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,They're hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:30.59,Main Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,Digging in!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.37,0:23:36.45,Italics Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,It's so juicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.03,0:23:41.56,Italics Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,The bun is soft and flaky, \Njust like pie crust!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:44.57,Italics Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,The meat stuffing has lots of sliced onions!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.57,0:23:46.82,Italics Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,The spicy black pepper adds a nice note.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.82,0:23:51.22,Italics Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,The ground pork's mild richness \Nand umami just keep gushing out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:53.82,Italics Dialogue,Women,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.19,0:23:56.50,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.50,0:23:58.60,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,Soma-kun, they seem to like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:23:59.04,Main Dialogue,S,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
