Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:11.01,sign_34670_523_The_Third_Plate,Sign2407,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Plate
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:11.01,sign_34670_524_Next_Episode__Mo,Sign2407,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode: {\fs20}Moon Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.18,0:24:10.51,Main Dialogue,M,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you savor the next episode!
